I gave it all I had, but these Hella Hot Outstanding Puffs just lit me up and my guy @lewishowes made sure I got cooled off with the quickness. S/O to @javalemcgee for all the great work he’s doing with his charity @juglifewater. 

I challenge @chriswharder, @edmylett & @mhiggins to the #HellaHotChallenge, a partnership between @outstandingfoods and @juglifewater to help raise awareness and encourage donations to bring clean drinking water to communities that need it most around the world. @outstandingfoods is matching all donations up to $10k 

Here's how you can participate:
1. Grab a friend, a cup of water and your Hella Hot Outstanding Puffs 🔥
2. Set up your camera and give your friend the cup of water 🚰
3. As soon as the 30 second timer begins, your friend becomes the judge. Hit go and start snacking, but keep that poker face! 😐
4. The second you crack, they get to throw the cup of water in your face… but, if you can last the full 30 seconds — snag that cup and throw the water on them 💦
5. When time is up (and one of you is wet), tell us the three or more people you’re challenging! 🏆
6. Post the video to your Instagram feed and/or TikTok and use the hashtag #HellaHotChallenge and tag both @outstandingfoods and @juglifewater as well as the 3+ others you challenged.

To learn more about the challenge hit the link in my bio and get involved 🙌🙌

My guy @joejonas challenged me to #saysomething about how I manage mental health in support of @one4theboys 

I do a lot of different things but the most effective thing I do is I use qualitative data to create a deeper self awareness about my own mental well being. It’s something I really believe in and love to share with people because it has really changed my life. 

Let’s keep pushing this mental health conversation. I challenge @lewishowes to #saysomething

I gave it all I had, but these Hella Hot Outstanding Puffs just lit me up and my guy @lewishowes made sure I got cooled off with the quickness. S/O to @javalemcgee for all the great work he’s doing with his charity @juglifewater. 

I challenge @chriswharder, @edmylett & @mhiggins to the #HellaHotChallenge, a partnership between @outstandingfoods and @juglifewater to help raise awareness and encourage donations to bring clean drinking water to communities that need it most around the world. @outstandingfoods is matching all donations up to $10k 

Here's how you can participate:
1. Grab a friend, a cup of water and your Hella Hot Outstanding Puffs 🔥
2. Set up your camera and give your friend the cup of water 🚰
3. As soon as the 30 second timer begins, your friend becomes the judge. Hit go and start snacking, but keep that poker face! 😐
4. The second you crack, they get to throw the cup of water in your face… but, if you can last the full 30 seconds — snag that cup and throw the water on them 💦
5. When time is up (and one of you is wet), tell us the three or more people you’re challenging! 🏆
6. Post the video to your Instagram feed and/or TikTok and use the hashtag #HellaHotChallenge and tag both @outstandingfoods and @juglifewater as well as the 3+ others you challenged.

To learn more about the challenge hit the link in my bio and get involved 🙌🙌

node.text:
Are you born an entrepreneur or do you become one? On this episode of #BuildwithRob this might be proof that you can be born one. My guest this week is the Natural Born Do-or-Dier @_matt.wan. Founder and CEO of @livemomentous, he was just eighteen when I helped him shape his vision for the worlds best supplement brand. Wise beyond his years, this young entrepreneur might as well be 40! 

@dyrdekmachine
